To use this module, you must explicitly declare some variables :

$samba_domain_name
$samba_netbios_name
$samba_listen_interface = "10.17.0.69/22"
$samba_homes = "false"

and if you use the ldap functionality also
$ldap_uri
$ldap_base
$ldap_admin_password



Not using the ldap functionality you still have to manualy create the smb users till I figure out a workaround for that .
